日間，向 iPhone 12、iPhone 12 mini 和 iPhone SE 的前 20,000 名購機者贈送限量的虎年限定 AirTag。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-694x324.png" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-694x324.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-1280x598.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-768x359.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-1536x718.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59-2048x957.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.21.59.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-694x316.png" alt="" width="694" height="316" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-694x316.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-1280x583.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-768x350.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-1536x700.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30-2048x934.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 6.23.30.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">優惠活動僅在日本境內提供，買家也必須通過官網或門店購買才可獲得禮物，在 Apple Store app 購買則沒有這項活動；官網更顯示，購買指定款的 Apple 商品更可獲得贈送的禮品卡優惠。若是購買 AirPods、AirPods Pro、AirPods Max，則可獲得面額 9000 日圓（約港幣 610 元）的 Apple 禮品卡；購買 Apple Watch Series 3、Apple Watch