</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>韓國全球首間「元宇宙返工」公司，打卡、開會、演講均於元宇宙內進行</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/29/first-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-com2us/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=first-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-com2us</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 29 Dec 2021 11:52:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Com2uS]]></category><category><![CDATA[Com2Verse]]></category><category><![CDATA[元宇宙]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078738</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>韓國遊戲公司 Com2uS 日前首次公開旗下開發中的元宇宙平台 《Com2Verse》的預告及試玩影片，展示了 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">韓國遊戲公司 Com2uS 日前首次公開旗下開發中的元宇宙平台 《Com2Verse》的預告及試玩影片，展示了在《Com2Verse》返工員工的一天。Com2uS 集團計畫將於 2022 年下半年，讓擁有 2,500 名員工的所有旗下公司入駐《Com2Verse》，正式開啟元宇宙返工、生活時代。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078739" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/b-Com2Verse-b-First-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-Com2uS-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/b-Com2Verse-b-First-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-Com2uS-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/b-Com2Verse-b-First-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-Com2uS-768x379.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/b-Com2Verse-b-First-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-Com2uS.png 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Com2Verse》 是把現實世界中的生活還原到網絡上的多功能元宇宙平台，遊戲將社會、文化、經濟等的現實世界系統搬進數碼世界，打造可以實現日常生活的虛擬空間。平台分為四個領域，包括提供智能辦公空間的 Office World（辦公世界）、提供金融、醫療、教育、流通等服務的 Commercial World（商業世界）、可供用戶享受遊戲、音樂、電影、表演等休閒的 Theme Park World（主題樂園世界），以及提供日常溝通及分享的 Community World（社區世界）。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078741" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-694x371.png" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-694x371.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-1280x684.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-768x410.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-1536x820.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01-2048x1094.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.01.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-694x377.png" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-694x377.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-1280x695.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-768x417.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-1536x834.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42-2048x1112.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.44.42.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（返工前的衝閘打卡，到電梯大堂可選擇層數）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078742" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-694x378.png" alt="" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-694x378.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-1280x697.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-768x418.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-1536x837.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44-2048x1116.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.07.44.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（在 Office World 辦公中使用日程表管理行程）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078743" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-694x378.png" alt="" width="694" height="378" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-694x378.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-1280x698.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-768x419.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-1536x837.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06-2048x1116.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.08.06.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（透過視訊和工作夥伴進行對話）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1078758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-694x381.png" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-694x381.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-1280x702.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-768x421.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-1536x843.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41-2048x1124.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕快照-2021-12-29-下午 5.45.41.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（可多人視訊進行小組會議/匯報，Office World 中可順暢操作辦公軟件如 PowerPoint）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">當中的 </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Office World 提供了不受物理距離影響的 Metaverse 工作環境，不論是日常開會、日程管理、文件處理等的功能一應俱全，工作更可通過視訊實現流暢快捷的溝通。 Com2us 總裁宋在俊、CMVO 總裁李柱煥、樸冠宇也出現在示範影片中，通過視訊對話，展示了 Com2Verse 中全新高效的辦公生活。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_49526"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0z2pjJTVa5w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">影片中亦顯示，每個用戶根據他們的活動和表現可獲得代幣獎勵，這預示著 Com2uS 集團目前正在開發由加密貨幣資助的項目的 Metanomics。Com2uS 計劃引入代幣經濟循環，</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">用戶作為元宇宙中生產和消費的主體的各種活動與經濟回報掛鉤，而這些經濟回報亦會帶出數字資產和服務等消費品。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Com2uS 表示，將於 2022 年下半年，讓擁有 2,500 名員工的所有旗下公司入駐《Com2Verse》，正式開啟元宇宙時代。同時，Com2uS 還在和各個行業的大型企業簽約，建設元宇宙生態系，未來將通過大量企業的入駐，打造集休閒、娛樂、經濟於一身的元宇宙都市。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_91017"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aqZFjRUyhvo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://game-news24.com/2021/12/28/b-com2verse-b-first-glance-at-metaverse-from-game-developer-com2us/">GN24</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
